{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC10_MER_040.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x70,
            "name_id": 0x36,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Miss, this medicine, how effective is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Oh, this? It's invigorating medicine,<CR>so I'm sure it differs from person to<CR>person..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6d,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "But its major effects treat headaches, chills, blurred vision, stiff shoulders and declining appetite due to aging."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x70,
            "name_id": 0x36,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Isn't that a bit too good to be true? I'm sure it can't be effective for everything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "But it is. Isn't that amazing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6d,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "In any case, a skilled apothecary combines secret ingredients to make this medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x70,
            "name_id": 0x36,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...if that's really true, then it is amazing. However, I just can't believe it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "(That's the medicine I synthesized...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x70,
            "name_id": 0x36,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "If you can, I'd like you to describe its effects to me in detail."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Sure thing, just wait here.<CR>Ayesha, switch!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Can you explain the effects of this medicine to this customer?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay. Well, this medicine uses nourishment from roots to improve your blood circulation..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "And it includes a component that cleanses the toxins in your blood."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "By cleaning your blood, it can reduce body pains and prevent chills."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x70,
            "name_id": 0x36,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Mmhm, I see. So that's how it works..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x70,
            "name_id": 0x36,
            "extra_id": 0x1f7,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Sounds good! I'll take one bottle of this medicine!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x70,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Okay, thank you for your patronage!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Thanks. That was a great help. Explanations from the expert sure are better."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x38,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, that was medicine that I made."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf8,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "But it's so disappointing that that was the last of your medicine!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf6,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Your medicine was such a great seller at our store that the owner is sad, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I see. I feel kinda bad now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Well, don't worry about it. You have something else to do, so it can't be helped."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "In exchange, if you start up your day job again, let me know, okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Yes, definitely."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "If you want, we can skip Ernie, and you can sell it directly to us..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I-I wonder if I can do that...<CR>I need to talk to Ernie first."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Hmhmhm, you're so cute when you're flustered. That was just a joke."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Not only our customers, but I use your medicine, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I'll be waiting for the day you return! Like, totally waiting!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Wh-When you exaggerate that much,<CR>I don't know what to say..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "But, I'll do my best. So please wait!"
        }
    ]
}